\c 95
\s Ukudumisa iN\nd kosi\nd*
\p
\v 1 Wozani, siyihlabelele iN\nd kosi\nd*, senze umsindo wentokozo\x + 95.2. Hlab. 47.1. 66.1. 81.1. 98.4,6. 100.1.\x* kulo idwala losindiso lwethu\x + 2 Sam. 22.47. Hlab. 94.22.\x*.
\v 2 Kasize phambi kobuso bayo ngokubonga, senze umsindo wentokozo kuyo ngezihlabelelo\x + 95.2. Hlab. 47.1. 66.1. 81.1. 98.4,6. 100.1.\x*.
\p
\v 3 Ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* inguNkulunkulu omkhulu\x + Eks. 18.11. Hlab. 96.4. 135.5.\x*, leNkosi enkulu phezu kwabonkulunkulu bonke\x + Hlab. 97.9.\x*.
\v 4 Okusesandleni sayo indawo zomhlaba ezizikileyo, lezingqonga zezintaba zingezayo\x + Nani 23.22.\x*.
\v 5 Olungolwayo ulwandle, yona-ke yalwenza\x + Gen. 1.9,10.\x*, lezandla zayo zabumba umhlabathi owomileyo\x + Gen. 1.9,10.\x*.
\p
\v 6 Wozani, sikhonze\x + Hlab. 45.11.\x* sikhothame\x + Hlab. 72.9.\x*, siguqe phambi kweN\nd kosi\x + 2 Lan. 6.13. Dan. 6.10.\x*\nd*, umenzi wethu\x + Hlab. 149.2. Hlab. 100.3. Dute. 32.6.\x*.
\v 7 Ngoba yona inguNkulunkulu wethu, thina-ke singabantu bedlelo layo\x + Hlab. 74.1.\x*, lezimvu zesandla sayo\x + Hlab. 80.1.\x*.
\p Lamuhla uba\x + Heb. 3.7-11, 15.4.7.\x* lilizwa ilizwi layo\x + Nani 14.22.\x*,
